# .js files committed alongside .ts so plugin install path works without npm install.
# `tsc -p tsconfig.build.json` regenerates them; release prerelease guard asserts parity.
#
# node_modules/ committed too (production deps only — yaml, cockatiel, nanoid;
# ~2.2 MB, 3 top-level dirs, zero transitive). Same reason: `/plugin install
# core@sutra` and `/plugin update core@sutra` ship a fully-working connectors
# stack with no first-call npm install. bump-version.sh refreshes node_modules
# pre-tag via `npm install --omit=dev` so each release carries fresh deps.
/dist/
*.tsbuildinfo
